extend layout
block content  
  p
    h4 Easy navigation of projects on <a href="http://github.com">Github</a>.
  p
    | (View the project in a file tray akin to TextMate or Sublime Text)

  - if (error)
    data-alert.alert-box.alert.round= message
  .row
    .large-12.columns
    form(method="POST", action="/project")
      input(type='text', placeholder='Enter a github project URL here', name="project")
      .row
        .large-12.columns
          input(type='submit', value="View Project", class="large button expand")
      
  p
    h5 Examples
  ul
    li 
      a(href="http://gitray.com/Jonovono/gitray") https://github.com/Jonovono/gitray
    li 
      a(href="http://gitray.com/Jonovono/c") Jonovono/c
    li 
      a(href="http://gitray.com/Clojure/clojurescript") Clojure clojurescript
  
  #footer
    p Or simply replace https://github.com with http://gitray.com
    p <img src="/img/github.png"/> ---> <img  src="/img/gitray.png"/>
    
